cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.LG 

This paper is about classification of social media data, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and multimedia analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related topics. The second likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which covers multimedia analysis and processing. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) and computer vision (CV) techniques, which suggest cs.IR and cs.CV as likely categories. Finally, the paper proposes simple models that combine information from different modalities, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (ML) and deep learning (DL), suggesting cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a possible category.
